OL,3,CPatient Safety Commissioner vows to
OL,4,Cmeet Galloway campaigners
OL,6,FScotland's first Patient Safety
OL,7,FCommissioner has said she will
OL,8,F"absolutely" visit health campaigners
OL,9,Fin Dumfries and Galloway.
OL,11,FKaren Titchener began the independent
OL,12,Frole this week, and is charged with
OL,13,Frepresenting the views and concerns of
OL,14,Fpatients, as well as improving health
OL,15,Foutcomes and safety.
OL,17,FIn an interview with Representing
OL,18,FBorder, she acknowledged the scale of
OL,19,Fthe challenges she faces, referring to
OL,20,Funderstaffing within the NHS and
OL,21,F"imploding" waiting times.
