OL,6,FThe law creating her role was passed
OL,7,Fby the Scottish Parliament in 2023,
OL,8,Fbut the recruitment process failed
OL,9,Ftwice.
OL,11,FInitial interviews failed to find a
OL,12,Fsuitable candidate, and a second round
OL,13,Fsaw the preferred person turn the job
OL,14,Fdown.
OL,16,FMrs Titchener said the fact the role
OL,17,Fwas difficult to recruit for "tells
OL,18,Fits own story", and shows how
OL,19,Fdifficult it will be for her to
OL,20,Fimprove experiences for patients.
