OL,6,FPeople in Dumfries and Galloway say
OL,7,Ftheir region faces unique challenges
OL,8,Fbecause of how rural it is.
OL,10,FAt a walking football tournament in
OL,11,FStranraer, Brian Balfour, who's in his
OL,12,Flate fifties, said he had been waiting
OL,13,Fmore than two years for a knee
OL,14,Foperation, and was "frustrated" and in
OL,15,Fpain.
