OL,6,FBobby McKie, who played more than 500
OL,7,Ftimes for Stranraer FC, said he felt
OL,8,Flucky to have recently had two knee
OL,9,Foperations, but spent nearly three
OL,10,Fyears waiting for the first, and
OL,11,Fanother eight months for the second.
OL,13,FHe told Representing Border that
OL,14,Fwaiting for surgery, which limited his
OL,15,Fability to play walking football,
OL,16,F"gets to your head a wee bit...
OL,17,Fdepression sets in".
