OL,6,FScotland's Health Secretary says the
OL,7,Fnumber of operations performed in July
OL,8,Fwas the highest in five years, showing
OL,9,Fan 8.9 percent increase compared to
OL,10,FJuly 2024.
OL,12,FHowever, recent statistics showed that
OL,13,Fwaits of over two years are now more
OL,14,Fthan 800 times higher in Scotland
OL,15,F(almost 15,000) than in England (182).
