OL,3,CPatient Safety Commissioner vows to
OL,4,Cmeet Galloway campaigners
OL,6,FThere was a particularly sharp jump of
OL,7,Faround 26 percent in the overall
OL,8,Fnumber of people waiting for new
OL,9,Foutpatient appointments in Dumfries
OL,10,Fand Galloway in the second quarter of
OL,11,F2025, compared to the same period in
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FNHS Dumfries & Galloway says it's
OL,15,Fcommitted to the national target that
OL,16,Fno one should wait longer than 52
OL,17,Fweeks for outpatient appointments, or
OL,18,Finpatient and day case procedures, by
OL,19,FMarch 2026.
