OL,3,CPatient Safety Commissioner vows to
OL,4,Cmeet Galloway campaigners
OL,6,FConcerns have also been raised about
OL,7,Faccess to maternity services.
OL,9,FBabies haven't been delivered at the
OL,10,FGalloway Community Hospital in
OL,11,FStranraer since 2018, due to a lack of
OL,12,Fstaff.
OL,14,FMost expectant mothers face a journey
OL,15,Fof around 70 miles to Dumfries to give
OL,16,Fbirth, and for some appointments.
OL,18,FClaire Fleming had her first baby,
OL,19,Fwhich was stillborn, in 2012.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
