OL,3,CPatient Safety Commissioner vows to
OL,4,Cmeet Galloway campaigners
OL,6,FShe says that she was supported
OL,7,Fthrough the trauma by "great" local
OL,8,Fmaternity services, but by the time
OL,9,Fshe had her fourth child in 2021, most
OL,10,Fservices had been stripped away from
OL,11,Fher local hospital.
OL,13,FAngela Armstrong, a retired medical
OL,14,Fpractitioner who now leads the
OL,15,FGalloway Community Hospital Action
OL,16,FGroup, says birthing services should
OL,17,Fbe restored at the facility.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
