OL,3,CPatient Safety Commissioner vows to
OL,4,Cmeet Galloway campaigners
OL,6,FHowever, NHS Dumfries and Galloway
OL,7,Fsays the opening of the Oak Tree
OL,8,FFamily Centre in 2020 means more
OL,9,Fmaternity care is taking place
OL,10,Flocally, and that home births are
OL,11,Foffered for low risk pregnancies in
OL,12,FGalloway.
OL,14,FEven if midwife-led birthing services
OL,15,Freturned to the hospital, the health
OL,16,Fboard argues high risk pregnancies,
OL,17,Fwhich account for most of the total
OL,18,Fand require consultant-led care, would
OL,19,Fstill need to take place at the
OL,20,FDumfries and Galloway Royal Infirmary.
