OL,3,CPatient Safety Commissioner vows to
OL,4,Cmeet Galloway campaigners
OL,6,FBoth Angela Armstrong and Claire
OL,7,FFleming said it was important for
OL,8,FScotland's new Patient Safety
OL,9,FCommissioner to visit Galloway, in
OL,10,Forder to hear about the issues facing
OL,11,Flocal people directly.
OL,13,FKaren Titchener told Representing
OL,14,FBorder she would "absolutely" visit
OL,15,Fthe Galloway Community Hospital Action
OL,16,FGroup, and stressed that patients in
OL,17,Frural areas should not have a lower
OL,18,Fstandard of care than those in urban
OL,19,Fareas.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
