OL,3,CPatient Safety Commissioner vows to
OL,4,Cmeet Galloway campaigners
OL,6,FShe said that as a nurse practitioner:
OL,7,F"If I was having a baby and the
OL,8,Fhospital was 70 miles away, I would be
OL,9,Fconcerned."
OL,11,FMrs Titchener pledged to hold health
OL,12,Fboards and the Scottish Government to
OL,13,Faccount, saying "I don't intend to be
OL,14,Ffaint-hearted", and asked members of
OL,15,Fthe public to judge her own record in
OL,16,Fa year's time.
